        " حَرٍّ شَدِيدٍ فَيَخَافُ عَلَى جَبْهَتِهِ مِنَ اَلْأَرْضِ قَالَ «يَضَعُ ثَوْبَهُ تَحْتَ جَبْهَتِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.801 - Abu Basir asked Him about a man praying in extreme heat and fearing for his forehead due to the hot ground.\nImam (as) replied: \"He should place his garment beneath his forehead”."
        ]
      }
